name: 阿尼尼斯卡·卢卡西亚克
name_full: 阿尼尼斯卡·卢卡西亚克 Agnieszka Lukasiak
introduction: Agnieszka Lukasiak (born 18 December 1979 in Wrocław, Poland) is an award-winning film director based in Los Angeles, Stockholm and London.[1] She began her career by directing cinema released feature documentaries. She is now directing feature films.Agnieszka LukasiakAgnieszkaLukasiakApr2011.jpgLukasiak in April 2011Born18 December 1979 (age 38)Wrocław, PolandOccupationDirectorLukasiak came to Sweden in 1984 with her parents as refugees. [2] She graduated from the directing department of the Polish National Film School in Łódź in 2002. [3]
